CS Grunt
The Coalition States Grunt is the rank-and-file soldier of the most powerful
human nation on Rifts Earth. Disciplined, well-equipped, and utterly loyal,
the CS Grunt forms the backbone of the Coalition military.

CS Grunts receive the standard Coalition military skill package including
Dead Boy armour familiarity and proficiency with Coalition weapons. They
choose from Military, Physical, Pilot, Technical, and W.P. categories.

Attribute requirements: IQ 6, PS 9, PE 9.
Starting equipment: Coalition Dead Boy armour, C-20 laser pistol,
C-12 heavy assault rifle, four grenades, and Coalition standard gear.
